{"tid":1726363,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"自動不推文script","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T13:40:16.000Z","uid":34664,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"877fad5b0c2a94cca233b7178a5aa5fbf883d97d","tid":1726363,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>效果</strong><br />\n你喺某一個post用過不推文之後<br />\n你一個月內再喺同一個post回覆嘅時候就會自動用不推文<br />\n對每一個post獨立生效<br />\n<br />\n<strong>注意</strong><br />\n1. <a href=\"http://呢個post同openuserjs.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%91%A2%E5%80%8Bpost%E5%90%8Copenuserjs.org&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=8254c649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">呢個post同openuserjs.org</a>喺唯一發佈同更新嘅地方，我唔會擺去其他網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 連登UI更新有機會令呢條script失效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 我寫得太廢都會失效，可能呢個post已經炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 連登自帶嗰個不推文popup我唔識整走佢，你每次撳回覆都會彈出嚟一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. browser only，冇得喺app用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>裝法</strong><br />\n首先裝Tampermonkey (其他同類userscript manager我冇測試過)<br />\nFirefox: <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fzh-TW%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Ftampermonkey%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=e38c0694\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/</a><br />\nChrome: <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Ftampermonkey%2Fdhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=8284b503\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo</a><br />\n<br />\n然後去呢度<br />\n撳Install就裝得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://openuserjs.org/scripts/lihkg_rotom/LIHKG_%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopenuserjs.org%2Fscripts%2Flihkg_rotom%2FLIHKG_%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%2587&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c7a7eb74\" target=\"_blank\">https://openuserjs.org/scripts/lihkg_rotom/LIHKG_%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%87</a></span><br />\n亦都歡迎各位睇source code<br />\n有咩寫得唔好嘅屌吓我"},{"pid":"983462464c85ea145a7b76f55ac4468f1398ed84","tid":1726363,"uid":34664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"裝完之後記得F5你睇緊嘅tabs"},{"pid":"725bb6dbd7fadeb18133ed4ef5cbb286de1d05be","tid":1726363,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cae4b3fdfbf51509d7d39211a2d56ec9b35881","tid":1726363,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b5344b5c26afbea09e4bb04c1cbac7af2a0697","tid":1726363,"uid":121636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb3e0261fb439904e2138a078fc66b6d94738159","tid":1726363,"uid":77542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"Thanks !"},{"pid":"bd7b3b9ed59c6427dd613c6be449e191d7f0def3","tid":1726363,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b804c2013e64763f6b526c092c808ced0222004","tid":1726363,"ui